---
title: Middle Eastern Style Prawn Stew with chickpeas, charred courgette and spiced bulgur
description: This Middle Eastern-inspired stew is bursting with amazing flavours. The harissa spiced prawns shine as the star of the show while the chickpeas, bulgur and veg all work together to make this a perfectly balanced and filling meal.
